<p align="center"><img src="images/logo.gif" width="300" height="100" alt="Kiddy Grade Logo" /><br />
<font size="+2">Kiddy Grade: E<font color="#666666">ncounter of</font> S<font color="#666666">hadow-Work</font></font>
<br /></p>

<p>Kiddy Grade is a 2002 Anime from Studio <a href="http://www.gonzo.co.jp/" target="_blank">Gonzo</a> (whose other titles include Vandread, Hellsing, Full Metal Panic, and Last Exile) and gímik (<a href="http://www.uta-kata.com/" target="_blank">Uta∽Kata</a>) about a pair of young girls with extraordinary powers working as secret agents for the Galactic Organisation of Trade and Tarrifs (GOTT). The series marked the directorial debut of <a href="http://goto.cute.or.jp/" target="_blank">Keiji Gotoh</a> (character designer for Martian Successor Nadesico and Gatekeepers). The series is licensed in the US (<a href="http://www.funimation.com/" target="_blank">FUNimation</a>), UK (<a href="http://www.mvm-uk.co.uk/" target="_blank">MVM</a>), Australia (<a href="http://www.madman.com.au/" target="_blank">Madman</a>), France (<a href="http://www.declic-images.com/" target="_blank">Déclic Images</a>), Germany (<a href="http://www.tokyopop.de/" target="_blank">Tokyopop</a>) and Taiwan (<a href="http://www.pimgroup.com.tw/" target="_blank">PIM</a>)</p>

<table width="50%"><tr><td>Official Sites:</td><td align="right"><a href="http://funimation.com/kiddygrade/" target="_blank">FUNimation</a> (US) / <a href="http://www.kiddygrade.com/" target="_blank">KiddyGrade -works on web-</a> (Japan)</td></tr></table>

